{"tid":216364,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[web桌遊]Secret Hitler(1)","createTime":"2017-04-25T06:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T14:06:43.000Z","uid":49571,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e86271ccd73a590a2f87d45fe48bc951cb6aa876","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"網址: <a href=\"http://onenightwerewolf.online/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fonenightwerewolf.online%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=27fdf52a\" target=\"_blank\">http://onenightwerewolf.online/</a><br />\n小弟id: pickballboy1<br />\n<br />\n本身係實體版桌遊, 而家出埋web版<br />\n玩悶左狼人, killer, 三國殺的巴打要試下咧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩法: <a href=\"http://www.damanwoo.com/node/87576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.damanwoo.com%2Fnode%2F87576&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=787adc09\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.damanwoo.com/node/87576</a><br />\n這個遊戲有三中方式分出勝負:<br />\n1.法西斯份子通過六張法案<br />\n2.自由派通過五張法案<br />\n3.在法西斯份子通過第三張的法案時候，如果擔任大法官的是希特勒，那遊戲就立即結束。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4.總統處死左希特勒</span> (編文寫漏左)"},{"pid":"0638c8c46cfac2e2fae4e5a20f0bf100d2d5947f","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.damanwoo.com/files/media/8/e/7/1/3/b/5/7/1/a/8e713b571aaa7179c9e94fc5b5d2aa80_original.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.damanwoo.com%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2F8%2Fe%2F7%2F1%2F3%2Fb%2F5%2F7%2F1%2Fa%2F8e713b571aaa7179c9e94fc5b5d2aa80_original.png&h=7fde356c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"accb88d3ba2da10338be214ec0ca3722c39d97b0","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.damanwoo.com/files/media/p/h/o/t/o/o/r/i/g/i/photo-original_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.damanwoo.com%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Fp%2Fh%2Fo%2Ft%2Fo%2Fo%2Fr%2Fi%2Fg%2Fi%2Fphoto-original_2.jpg&h=bb9098f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.damanwoo.com/files/media/s/c/r/e/e/n/s/h/o/t/screenshot-2015-11-24-at-5.43.10-pm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.damanwoo.com%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Fs%2Fc%2Fr%2Fe%2Fe%2Fn%2Fs%2Fh%2Fo%2Ft%2Fscreenshot-2015-11-24-at-5.43.10-pm.jpg&h=43add505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.damanwoo.com/files/media/s/e/c/r/e/t/h/i/t/l/secret-hitler-600x338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.damanwoo.com%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Fs%2Fe%2Fc%2Fr%2Fe%2Ft%2Fh%2Fi%2Ft%2Fl%2Fsecret-hitler-600x338.jpg&h=cd947d41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7adb00a1cfa6f6f3f31bb99c630bb95ce53288c","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"多人玩可開香港場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8950c50a70a60aa08ac280b76fef908a0727a3","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"遊戲規則其實很簡單，在遊戲一開始，每個玩家都會先抽到一張代表法西斯主義或者是自由派的分類牌。而這個牌只有玩家自己能知道。<br />\n接著，所有人先閉上眼睛，然後由一指定主持人先要請法西斯主義者睜開眼睛。而希特勒必須要表明自己的身份。然後，所有人睜開眼睛 &mdash; 這個時候只有法西斯份子知道自己的同夥是誰，但自由派不知道。<br />\n <br />\n接下來，隨便先由一位玩家開始第一局。在這局中，這位玩家首先擔任&rdquo;總統候選人&rdquo;並且他會有個寫著&rdquo;總統&rdquo;的立牌在桌上。接著，他會指定另外一位玩家當&rdquo;大法官候選人&rdquo;。在這個時候，所有的玩家必須依照自己的判斷決定要不要讓這一組搭當當選。如果當選的話才會有接下來的步驟;反之則由下一位玩家擔任候選人並且重覆上述動作。"},{"pid":"9620f22f7a39010837e581ec97c483c4746aabfe","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"當終於有一組總統與大法官搭當當選後，總統要做的下一件事就是從一疊各自代表&rdquo;法西斯有利&rdquo;以及&rdquo;自由派有利&rdquo;的牌之中，抽出三張來。這三張牌各自是什麼只有總統本人知道，然後他必須要先捨棄一張，並且把剩下的兩張交給大法官。而大法官要從這兩張牌再選出一張，當做最終的法案。"},{"pid":"f2d02c127f4eaf00b8b51ee61e94addb0c67bde6","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"這個遊戲有四種方式分出勝負:<br />\n1.法西斯份子通過六張法案<br />\n2.自由派通過五張法案<br />\n3.在法西斯份子通過第三張的法案時候，如果擔任大法官的是希特勒，那遊戲就立即結束。<br />\n4.總統處死左希特勒 (編文寫漏左)"},{"pid":"c64eaaef41cc9bd661a0f939baf48e8a4beb338f","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"不知道寫到這裡，大家是不是都已經昏頭了?不，還有更有意思的設定在後面:<br />\n每當有一張法西斯法案通過之後，都會有一件特別的事可以做:<br />\n <br />\n第二張法案通過時，總統都可以檢查任何一位玩家的身份。<br />\n第三張法案通過時，總統可以直接指名下位總統候選人。<br />\n第四與第五張法案通過時，每次總統必須要處決一個人。<br />\n所以到這裡，總統極有可能幹掉自己人，或者法西斯份子可以盡情的宰掉對方陣營的人。可憐的自由派，被人宰了都不知道怎麼死的&hellip;&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n大致了解整個遊戲最重要的精神是什麼了嗎?就是信任，猜忌，勾心鬥角，團結，或破壞團結。因為自由派的人在過程中不知道誰是朋友誰是敵人，那就只能靠每一次的法案來判斷;但法案又不是可以100%由自由派來決定的，就像先前說的，如果他抽到兩張都是法西斯的話，那他真是百口莫辯了。<br />\n而另一方面，法西斯要盡可能的誤導，誘惑自由派做出錯誤的決定，甚至是要想辦法讓他們窩裡反，幹掉自己人。"},{"pid":"9a5ebab25f6bb22b4d3aba71a8530f4fda4d1ee9","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"OBJECT<br />\n<br />\nEvery player has a secret identity as a member of either the Liberal team or the Fascist team. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Players on the Liberal team win if either:<br />\nFive Liberal Policies are enacted OR<br />\nHitler is assassinated.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Players on the Fascist team win if either:<br />\nSix Fascist Policies are enacted OR<br />\nHitler is elected Chancellor any time after the third Fascist Policy has been enacted.</span>"},{"pid":"a6bac31fe4202815a471f7c2dead82236f31339d","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"17 .......... Policy tiles (6 Liberal, 11 Fascist)"},{"pid":"b9b5a52a71386e5f035697042e40e63f62d32cfc","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"# PLAYERS\t5\t6\t7\t8\t9\t10<br />\nLiberals\t3\t4\t4\t5\t5\t6<br />\nFascists\t1+H\t1+H\t2+H\t2+H\t3+H\t3+H"},{"pid":"4c206ee8cd4916a9de552c8520a4bb8883bb94bd","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ymtls4ep\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fymtls4ep&h=071d11c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ecca1fafad52c7f0686aae78b945c1db82633bd","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"TRATEGY NOTES<br />\n<br />\nEveryone should claim to be a Liberal.<br />\n<br />\nIf this is your first time playing Hitler, just remember: be as Liberal as possible. <br />\n<br />\nLiberals frequently benefit from slowing play down and discussing the available information. Fascists frequently benefit from rushing votes and creating confusion.<br />\n<br />\nFascists most often win by electing Hitler, not by enacting six Policies! <br />\n<br />\nAsk other players to explain why they took an action.<br />\n<br />\nIf a Fascist Policy comes up, there are only three possible culprits: The President, the Chancellor, or the Policy Deck. Try to figure out who (or what!) put you in this position."},{"pid":"585f9c3f05d36e6382c16fe5dec00fcc343f37cb","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846dbcc8b27942b9409769fa94a8633587669f6b","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:59:59.000Z","msg":"雖然係英文, 但好易上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303b384dccc3d4e273c0ce221ad0aac0f024a320","tid":216364,"uid":49571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"telegram版都有, 不過web版方便新手用"},{"pid":"db8ff78